{"tid":2282910,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被指涉旺角「私了」清路障女護 女子被裁罪名成立 判監17星期","createTime":"2020-11-12T07:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T20:31:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"6817842ab680ee84f600653ba857d6a4d669528e","tid":2282910,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20201029-0520copy_JArBT_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20201029-0520copy_JArBT_1200x0.png&h=bd1691b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11252\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F11252&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au5q%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=b28ddc5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11252</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第九庭<br />\n#鍾明新裁判官<br />\n#1013旺角 #判刑🔥<br />\n<br />\n盧(40) 已還押14日🛑<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1)參與非法集結 🛑罪名成立<br />\n被控於19年10月13日，在旺角彌敦道及亞皆老街交界，連同其他身分不詳的人參與非法集結<br />\n(3)普通襲擊 🛑已認罪<br />\n被控於同日在彌敦道及旺角道交界襲擊女子 何潤姿<br />\n<br />\n‼️‼️速報‼️‼️<br />\n<br />\n判刑如下：<br />\n控罪（1): 15星期即時監禁<br />\n控罪（3): 3星期即時監禁<br />\n<br />\n部分刑期同期執行，合共17 星期監禁。<br />\n<br />\n詳情後補"},{"pid":"6ad27f221398299cd9d5e8a45576201efae00cc9","tid":2282910,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3fe4bc0d18747fb7b0d40f41577e71ab5cbfe1","tid":2282910,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:52:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf64c74d75c5b7c87300d9c3784e9933d1b2474","tid":2282910,"uid":140737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:52:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f63d2865749faa63d6c2a8580e0f519f30efbc6","tid":2282910,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae73318fea87a915aa78eca0a11fca5df4136fe","tid":2282910,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:55:28.000Z","msg":"補充:<br />\n判刑如下：<br />\n控罪（1): 15星期即時監禁<br />\n控罪（3): 4.5星期即時監禁<br />\n<br />\n被告承認第三控罪，獲扣減三分一刑期，即第三控罪判處3星期監禁。<br />\n<br />\n法庭指未有其他扣減刑期的因素，而第三控罪的其中1星期與第一控罪同期執行，合共17 星期即時監禁。"},{"pid":"d4484e49ba066c86d5d437b730b9f7d92b76716e","tid":2282910,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:55:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3d58702f6f3870c434649c801f5aabf780d7e6","tid":2282910,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:56:39.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11cd4150d472e761213c8dc4f527b09f278528d6","tid":2282910,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935c942733f69922153f94baebdc947768c57fc8","tid":2282910,"uid":33263,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T07:57:15.000Z","msg":"的士司機撞人 唔洗告<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個就